Citation.sAbstract: In the present paper, a study of temperature behaviour of the liquid liquid equilibrium in ternary systems N,N-dimethylformamide + 2- methylpentane + methanol and N,N-dimethylformamide + methylcyclohexane + methanol. The analysis of critical curves of the liquid liquid equilibrium by means of the regular solution model was carried out. The acquired predictions were subsequently verified experimentally.
Citation.sTitle: Liquid liquid equilibrium in ternary systems N,N-dimethylformamide + 2-methylpentane + methanol and N,N-dimethylformamide + methylcyclohexane + methanol
